Clinton Pledges U.S., EU Will Take Initiatives to Quell Violence in Syria

-- B y   F l a v i a   K r a u s e - J a c k s o n
-- 
2011-05-17T14:44:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/u-s-eu-to-take-further-steps-on-syria.html
U.S. Secretary of State  Hillary
Clinton  and European Union foreign policy chief  Catherine Ashton 
promised further action to quell violence in  Syria .  “I am very worried about what’s happened in the past
days,” Ashton said. “It’s extremely alarming. Now is a
situation where we need to consider all options.”  Ashton and Clinton both indicated there would be further
initiatives in “coming hours and days.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Flavia Krause-Jackson at 
 fjackson@bloomberg.net  